\int_{\mathbb{R}}T(f)(x)g(x)dx=\int_{\mathbb{R}}\Big(\int_{\mathbb{R}}f(t)e^{-ixt}dt\Big)g(x)dx=\int_{\mathbb{R}}\int_{\mathbb{R}}f(t)g(x)e^{-ixt}dtdx=\int_{\mathbb{R}}\int_{\mathbb{R}}f(t)g(x)e^{-ixt}dxdt=\int_{\mathbb{R}}f(t)\Big(\int_{\mathbb{R}}g(x)e^{-ixt}dx\Big)dt=\int_{\mathbb{R}}f(t)T(g)(t)dt
